title: Ep - 16 - Ladies of London
description:
Julie Montagu and Sophie Stanbury from Ladies of London provide inside scoop on the show, Kate’s friend Andrew is forced to watch the season finale of Rob and Chyna, and Kate and her friend Cara dissect an episode of Dance Moms.
